headline: Why This Analyst Says It's Time To 'Accumulate' Shares As This Top Nuclear Stock Falls Despite Surprise 20% Profit Gain
summary: BWX Technologies, the U.S. Navy's main nuclear reactor supplier, reported better-than-expected third-quarter earnings and revenue and once more raised its full-year profit outlook after Monday's stock market.
